RENTSTRIKE: E N D G A M E

// Every campaign needs a solid strategy to win. We need information, we need ideas, we need demands, and we need to win.

// We've devised an fun, interactive strategy game, which will hopefully equip participants with enough concrete ideas to take back to their campuses and workplaces. We want to support existing struggles and prepare people for the struggles around the corner.

// But this will also be an exercise for the imagination: the future is full of uncertainties, and endless variables that we need to be prepared to tackle and use to our advantage.

// We promise radical fun, endless ideas of how to reach rent strike revolution, and lots and lots of consensus based decision making.
